Happy birthday to my #1, @ernest !! It is hard to believe I was there for your 21st birthday. You’ve become an amazing musician, artist, visionary, leader and inspiration to others. But most importantly, you’re dedicated to your friends and a loving father Ryman can look up to. I hope you know how loved you are by me and those around you ❤️‍🔥🐐

On the first morning of this year, I was informed that my Cosmo was killed in a tragic accident at home while we were out of town. It is no secret how much I loved this soul. He was so young and full of life, it is heartbreaking to accept that our time together was cut short. I wanted to share this for no other reason than to remember him in his element. He is an irreplaceable member of our family and will be deeply missed 🤍
